1177
01:30:22,760 --> 01:30:23,760
Não fale Pābā perto de mim.

1178
01:30:24,760 --> 01:30:26,760
Pābā-san,

1179
01:30:26,760 --> 01:30:27,760
Over-san,

1180
01:30:27,760 --> 01:30:28,760
Pābā-san,

1181
01:30:28,760 --> 01:30:30,760
Kōra.

1182
01:30:30,760 --> 01:30:32,760
Eu pensei:

1183
01:30:32,760 --> 01:30:34,760
Se ele se aproximar para atacar,

1184
01:30:34,760 --> 01:30:35,760
não vai notar.

1185
01:30:35,760 --> 01:30:37,760
Aí, quem não puder matar, morre.

1186
01:30:37,760 --> 01:30:38,760
Mas isso

1187
01:30:40,760 --> 01:30:41,760
